official_title: A joint resolution to authorize the Secretary of the Interior to assist in the restoration and preservation of certain historic properties known as Strawberry Banke, Inc.

summary.text: Authorizes the Secretary of the Interior to assist in the restoration and preservation of historic properties known as Strawberry Banke, Incorporated, New Hampshire. Authorizes appropriations of not to exceed $2,900,000 to carry out the provisions of this resolution.
